---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
---

<LandingLayout title="Terms">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="space-y-20 py-16">
      <header class="space-y-8 text-center border-b border-border/50 pb-12">
        <div className="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Legal & Compliance
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight">Terms of Use</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-muted-foreground max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Service terms, user responsibilities, and important disclaimers for our fertility awareness platform.</p>
        <div className="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 mt-8 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          <span>Last updated: January 2025</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>Governed by applicable law</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed space-y-12">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50/50 to-orange-50/50 dark:from-amber-950/20 dark:to-orange-950/20 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
            <span>⚠️</span>
            <span>Important: Not Medical Advice</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-foreground mb-4">
            Using this service means you agree to these terms
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6">
            Please read them carefully to understand your rights and responsibilities.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
              <span class="text-amber-500 mt-1">✗</span>
              <span class="text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200 font-medium">Not medical advice</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
              <span class="text-amber-500 mt-1">✗</span>
              <span class="text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200 font-medium">No guarantees</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
              <span class="text-amber-500 mt-1">✗</span>
              <span class="text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200 font-medium">Not healthcare</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-destructive/5 p-6 rounded-xl border border-destructive/20">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-destructive mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-destructive">🚫</span>
              No guarantees
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-red-700 dark:text-red-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-destructive">•</span>
                <span>Accuracy in all situations</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-destructive">•</span>
                <span>Outcomes or specific results</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-destructive">•</span>
                <span>Suitability for any purpose</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-destructive">
              Biological systems are complex and variable.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-secondary/30 p-6 rounded-xl border border-secondary/50">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">👤</span>
              Your responsibility
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-primary">•</span>
                <span>Information you enter</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-primary">•</span>
                <span>How you interpret results</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-primary">•</span>
                <span>Decisions based on the information</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-primary/5 p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary/20">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-primary">🔐</span>
            Account security
          </h3>
          <p class="text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 mb-4">
            You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account access.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span>Keep your login credentials secure</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span>Do not share access with others</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
              <span>Report any unauthorized access immediately</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-muted/30 p-6 rounded-xl border">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Service availability</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            The service is provided on a best-effort basis. Features may change, be interrupted, or discontinued over time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-muted/30 p-6 rounded-xl border">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Limitation of liability</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            To the extent permitted by law, we are not liable for any direct or indirect consequences arising from the use of, or inability to use, the service.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-muted/30 p-6 rounded-xl border text-center">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Questions about these terms?</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
            We're here to help clarify anything that's unclear.
          </p>
          <a
            href="mailto:support@canihavesex.today"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors"
          >
            <span>📧</span>
            Contact support
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LandingLayout>